{"html": [{"t": "<div><br><div class=\"p\">AUTORIZA EMISOR ELECTR&#xD3;NICO</div><br></div>", "i": 9206237}, {"t": "<div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Extracto de resoluci&#xF3;n exenta del Servicio de Impuestos Internos N&#xBA; 131, de 17 de noviembre de 2011, que autoriza a contribuyentes como emisores electr&#xF3;nicos.</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Se autoriza como emisor de documentos tributarios a contribuyentes RUT 91.253.000-0, RUT 77.085.350-8, RUT 76.363.060-9, RUT 70.009.410-3, RUT 76.281.300-9, RUT 76.130.867-K, RUT 76.139.472-K, RUT 76.043.567-8, RUT 96.987.290-0, RUT 7.128.065-9, RUT 76.424.440-0, RUT 76.341.000-5, RUT 76.111.113-2, RUT 76.013.705-7, RUT 76.201.640-0, RUT 96.828.080-5, RUT 77.687.700-K, RUT 76.150.998-5, RUT 78.903.750-7, RUT 84.940.400-8, RUT 76.107.839-9, RUT 76.071.893-9, RUT 81.697.200-0, RUT 96.986.680-3, RUT 76.961.000-6, RUT 76.077.049-3, RUT 96.596.370-7, RUT 76.011.319-0, RUT 96.803.690-4, RUT 96.631.740-K, RUT 96.729.820-4, RUT 96.817.230-1, RUT 96.830.390-2, RUT 78.054.800-2, RUT 15.261.240-0, RUT 15.584.324-1, RUT 77.637.790-2, RUT 96.792.310-9, RUT 84.915.900-3, RUT 76.037.103-3, RUT 78.919.390-8, RUT 86.598.000-0, RUT 76.664.080-K, RUT 76.164.923-K, RUT 99.571.920-7, RUT 76.127.226-8, RUT 76.031.529-K, RUT 88.543.300-6, RUT 79.530.710-9, RUT 76.125.457-K, RUT 76.125.459-6, RUT 76.500.210-9, RUT 76.860.170-4, RUT 76.498.520-6, RUT 96.997.550-5, RUT 14.355.355-8, RUT 5.093.648-1, RUT 79.561.860-0, RUT 79.752.350-K, RUT 77.845.090-9, RUT 76.713.540-8, RUT 76.117.165-8, RUT 96.877.760-2, RUT 78.980.730-2, RUT 78.595.710-5, RUT 76.385.020-K, RUT 59.147.250-K, RUT 10.827.544-8, RUT 76.010.542-2, RUT 76.042.939-2, RUT 9.748.681-6, RUT 76.072.949-3, RUT 76.062.680-5, RUT 86.100.500-3, RUT 76.065.788-3, RUT 76.123.917-1, RUT 78.431.510-K, RUT 76.057.958-0, RUT 76.131.858-6, RUT 76.083.144-1, RUT 79.875.160-3, RUT 77.849.090-0, RUT 76.317.590-1, RUT 76.141.817-3, RUT 76.775.710-7, RUT 52.005.492-8, RUT 76.670.550-2, RUT 76